{
  "stem": "935.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He drove around on his motorbike, Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Kommandant, in a white, little fur coat in summer, in August, all through the camp, having a ball.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He had everything a little child can have, except his parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So you see, the kommandant stole too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He stole the little gypsy boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had very little time to find out what happened to somebody else, really.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, it was a moment to moment thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had a show there too, by the way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't participate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had-- the Polish, most of the Polish, put on a show in that little round thing where they had the coffee, what they called coffee, thing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was one night when they had-- they sang folk songs from their shtetl, things like this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a mother and twins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was in the middle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they sang-- I don't know whether you know it, it used to be a very famous song-- 'Yiddishe Momme,' Sophie Tucker.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And even so, I used to have it in my repertoire, long before.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I've never heard it, not even from Sophie Tucker, singed that way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Than these two children, about 14, 15-year-old twins, sang the 'Yiddishe Momme.' And just before the end, an SS guard walked in, and took out the mother.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The next day, the bookkeeper in the block, who had to cross off the names every day of those who didn't live anymore, told me that an order had come that everyone over 40 had to go into the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was the mother's 40th birthday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Now, she knew, and the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They kept-- she walked out beautiful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "No tears, very, very straight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the children finished the song.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
